Features:

i)    Can upload a picture from computer
      ==> Upload Controller

ii)   Can display uploaded picture on the page
      ==> Main Controller

iii)  Can store uploaded picture in a database
      ==> Backend code

iv)   Can retrieve all uploaded pictures from
      database
      ==> LoadController




Strategy:
- Work quickly
- Tackle things I like first i.e
